name: READY TO CLAY
description: I dedicated almost my whole life to make digital cover art for rap music industry; this last year I find myself spirituality and artistically doing a new style of hand-made visuals and entering into the NFT world. I don't want to do bad-payed work for labels n companys anymore, I want to do this for me and for people who really appreciate what I do. This "Ready to Clay" NFT (the first I ever do) is a tribute to the old me and to Biggie Smalls and his album "READY TO DIE", that's how I feel everyday. Ready to die and ready to live. <3
